Version 4.6.3 (2026/06/08)
* Fixed an uncommon Lua error caused by faulty event ordering assumptions

Version 4.6.2 (2026/05/12)
* Minor tweaks and polishing for the pledge calendar

Version 4.6.1 (2026/05/11)
* Fixed a Lua error that can arise if the optional LibQuestStatus is installed,
  but the optional LibUndauntedPledges is missing

Version 4.6.0 (2026/05/11)
* Added support for the optional LibQuestStatus and LibServerResetTime
  libraries, which enables the following features:
  - Hovering over a dungeon in the pledge calendar will now display additional
    information about the pledge and skill point status of characters
  - Entering a dungeon that is one of the day's pledges will now display a
    notification if the character does not have the pledge quest and has not
    completed the pledge for the day
  - The tooltips for trial quest items will now show information related to the
    weekly coffer cooldown

Version 4.5.5 (2026/05/05)
* Updated the ESO Clears Bot QR code to include Opulent Ordeal

Version 4.5.4 (2026/04/27)
* Updated trial motif achievements to match the changes in Update 50

Version 4.5.3 (2026/04/16)
* Improved the handling of keybinds for UI interactions

Version 4.5.2 (2026/04/16)
* Added safeguard against errors from old embedded/non-manifested LibAddonMenu2

Version 4.5.1 (2026/03/20)
* Added a Screenshot Mode button to the upper-right corner of the Achievements
  Tracker, in response to feedback that the existing method of activating
  Screenshot Mode had poor discoverability

Version 4.5.0 (2026/03/18)
* Added support for the ESO Clears Bot; if the optional LibQRCode is installed,
  a QR code compatible with the ESO Clears Bot will be displayed in the
  Screenshot Mode for dungeon and trial achievements

Version 4.4.0 (2026/02/23)
* Added support for Opulent Ordeal
* Added the option to assign a keybind to leaving an instance
  - This is intended to be a less cumbersome alternative to pressing "P-T-E"
  - As a safeguard against accidental keypresses, the keybind must be used twice
    in quick succession
* The automatic rejoining of a group will now work for kicks, in addition to
  disband reformations

Version 4.3.3 (2025/09/18)
* Repositioning of the status bar is now handled by LibCombatAlerts

Version 4.3.2 (2025/07/10)
* Added support for Naj-Caldeesh and Black Gem Foundry

Version 4.3.1 (2025/06/24)
* Improved the display of subclassing information in the History Browser

Version 4.3.0 (2025/06/09)
* Your character's selection of class skill lines will now be recorded in the
  score history, visible in the popup that appears when mousing over an entry in
  the History Browser
* Added Spanish localization by Cisneros

Version 4.2.7 (2025/04/21)
* Added support for Ossein Cage

Versions 4.2.5 to 4.2.6 (2025/03/11)
* Corrected achievement-related information for Exiled Redoubt and Lep Seclusa,
  to reflect a couple of changes ZOS made between the final PTS and live release

Version 4.2.4 (2025/01/29)
* Added support for Exiled Redoubt and Lep Seclusa

Version 4.2.3 (2024/09/19)
* API version bump for Update 44

Version 4.2.2 (2024/08/27)
* Fixed an issue with the achievements overview tooltip for Infinite Archive
  overflowing the available vertical screen space
* The time that is displayed in the note editing dialog, accessed by clicking on
  entries in the History Browser, will now include milliseconds

Version 4.2.1 (2024/08/25)
* Fixed a minor issue that can sometimes occur when using keybinds to switch to
  some base-game interfaces

Version 4.2.0 (2024/08/22)
* Added two new features related to Undaunted Pledges, if the optional
  LibUndauntedPledges library is installed
  - Added a "Today's Pledges" filter option for the Dungeons category of the
    Achievements Tracker
  - Added a 30-day pledge calendar, which can be accessed via the /pledgecal
    chat command, a custom keybind, or a button next to the Achievements
    Tracker's Screenshot Mode button
* Standardized tooltip text colors across all Extended Journal addons

Version 4.1.1 (2024/08/17)
* The Achievements Tracker can now be accessed by the /rat chat command

Version 4.1.0 (2024/08/16)
* Added a search filter to the Achievements Tracker for the names of content,
  their release years, and the names of their associated achievements
  - For example, you can find Stone Garden by searching for "stone garden", or
    by searching for "2020", or by searching for "genius" (for the "True Genius"
    achievement).
* Added a Screenshot Mode function to the Achievements Tracker
  - The button to access Screenshot Mode is located in the lower-left corner of
    the screen
* Updated LibExtendedJournal to facilitate potential Perfect Pixel support

Version 4.0.0 (2024/08/13)
* Raidificator 4 introduces the tracking of achievements for dungeons, trials,
  and arenas
  - Raidificator can even track achievements across different servers and
    accounts if the optional LibMultiAccountAchievements library is installed

Version 3.4.0 (2024/07/22)
* Added the ability to save notes in the History Browser
  - Clicking on an entry in the History Browser will display a dialog to create
    or edit a note for that entry
  - Notes can be viewed in the information tooltips that appear when mousing
    over entries in the History Browser
* The role selections for group members (e.g., tank, etc.) will now be recorded
  and can be viewed in the information tooltips that appear when mousing over
  entries in the History Browser
* Markers indicating whether the score in Infinite Archive is classified as solo
  or duo have been added to both the status panel and the History Browser
* Added a filter option to the History Browser's display of Infinite Archive
  entries to hide runs that did not progress beyond Arc 1

Versions 3.3.6 to 3.3.7 (2024/07/16)
* The status panel for Infinite Archive will now appear only after the timer has
  been started by someone entering the Archival Wings, similar to how trials and
  arenas are handled
  - This also has the effect of preventing the automatic logging feature from
    logging instances where the player is only visiting the vendors in the index
* Fixed a race-condition issue that could sometimes impede the function of the
  quest handling feature
* To work around the reported but still unresolved issues with how the esologs
  website processes log sessions, the encounter log for a completed trial will
  not be stopped until the player has left the trial instance

Version 3.3.5 (2024/07/11)
* Added an informational section about Reform Group to the settings panel to
  improve the discoverability of this feature
* Added Chinese localization by FusRoDah

Version 3.3.4 (2024/07/08)
* The trial completion chat message now includes a link to open the History
  Browser

Version 3.3.3 (2024/06/01)
* Fixed an issue with the dungeon timer sometimes failing to start in Unhallowed
  Grave

Version 3.3.2 (2024/04/17)
* Added support for Lucent Citadel

Version 3.3.1 (2024/01/29)
* Added support for Oathsworn Pit and Bedlam Veil

Version 3.3.0 (2023/10/24)
* Added a new feature to block the accidental in-combat casts of certain
  abilities in dungeons, trials, and arenas that are slotted for only their
  passive bonuses; this feature is disabled by default and can be enabled via
  the addon's settings panel
* Upon the completion of scored content, the History Browser will now
  automatically select that content

Version 3.2.0 (2023/10/10)
* It is now possible to anchor the status bar's position along its right edge
  instead of its left edge
  * While repositioning the status bar, a marker will appear on either the
    left or right edges of the status bar indicating the edge that will serve
    as the positioning anchor
  * To change which edge of the status bar will serve as the positioning
    anchor, you just need to briefly touch that edge of the status bar to the
    edge of the screen while repositioning the status bar

Versions 3.1.0 to 3.1.1 (2023/10/04)
* Added German localization by @ninibini
* Added options for handling the joining of dungeon, trial, or arena quests
  that are currently in-progress
* Updated the icons for the Endless Archive to match the changes in PTS 9.2.2
* Addressed an edge case where a long load screen could potentially prevent
  the dungeon timer from resetting when queueing into a new instance of the
  same dungeon

Version 3.0.2 (2023/09/29)
* Fixed an issue where Raidificator could erroneously stop an encounter log
  that it did not start

Version 3.0.1 (2023/09/28)
* Improved the formatting of the Group Members tooltip in the History Browser

Version 3.0.0 (2023/09/27)
* Raidificator 3 is a complete rewrite of the addon from scratch; this addon
  is now a member of the Extended Journal family of addons
* Added support for Endless Dungeons
* Merged the Dungeon Timer addon; that addon is now obsolete and has been
  discontinued
* Merged the Dungeon and Trial Instance Reset Tool addon; that addon is now
  obsolete and has been discontinued
